<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">فِيهِ مَسَائِلُ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">الأُولَى:</span> تَحْذِيرُ النَّاسِ مِنَ َالغُلُوِّ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">الثَّانِيَةُ:</span> مَا يَنْبَغِي أَنْ يَقُولَ مَنْ قِيلَ لَهُ: <span class="c2">(أَنْتَ سَيِّدُنَا)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">الثَّالِثَةُ:</span> قَولُهُ: <span class="c2">((لَا يَسْتَجْرِيَنَّكُمُ الشَّيطَانُ)</span>) مَعَ أَنَّهُمْ لَمْ يَقُولُوا إِلَّا الحَقَّ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">الرَّابِعَةُ:</span> قَولُهُ: <span class="c2">((مَا أُحِبُّ أَنْ تَرْفَعُونِي فَوقَ مَنْزِلَتِي)</span>).<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>